================================================================================
                      DEPLOYMENT OPTIONS
================================================================================

RECOMMENDED (Easiest):
  Frontend: Netlify or Vercel (static hosting)
  Backend: Render or Railway (Node.js hosting)
  Database: AWS RDS (managed PostgreSQL)
  Cost: $0-50/month

ALTERNATIVE (DIY):
  All on single VPS: DigitalOcean, AWS EC2, Linode
  Docker containerized
  Cost: $5-50/month

SIMPLE (Static Only):
  GitHub Pages (React build only)
  Archive all API data as JSON
  Cost: Free

