================================================================================
                       KEY FILES TO UPDATE
================================================================================

Before running npm start, update:
  /ormconfig.json
    - Change "username": "XXX" → "vaccovid_user"
    - Change "password": "XXX" → "test123"
    - KEEP "synchronize": false (read-only mode)

Optional (for fresh news):
  /app/src/config/secretData.ts
    - Add News API key (optional, archived news by default)

================================================================================
                        QUICK COMMANDS
================================================================================

Setup:
  brew install postgresql@15
  brew services start postgresql@15
  createdb vaccovid
  psql -U postgres -c "CREATE USER vaccovid_user WITH PASSWORD 'test123';"

Run:
  npm start              # Backend + Frontend together
  npm start --prefix client  # Frontend only
  node build/index.js    # Backend only

Test:
  curl http://localhost:5000/vaccines/all
  open http://localhost:3000

Debug:
  lsof -t -i tcp:3000,5000 | xargs kill -9  # Kill port conflicts
  psql -U vaccovid_user -d vaccovid          # Test DB connection

